{"id": "ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 199, "displayName": {"text": "Sichuan Street Food (当代川菜)", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cVdVSmhjSE14UlhKRFpGSTBabU5vV25Kd2JuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is absolutely delicious. The Sichuan food is so authentic. The lamb with cumin was exactly to my taste.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is absolutely delicious. The Sichuan food is so authentic. The lamb with cumin was exactly to my taste.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yeji Shawn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104889985864411916058/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2Q0-yQr7wJj-OL5nKp__p_3jtSfixCCXyPK0qXxnuMNvHh1eR=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-27T07:47:21.535712321Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cVdVSmhjSE14UlhKRFpGSTBabU5vV25Kd2JuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cVdVSmhjSE14UlhKRFpGSTBabU5vV25Kd2JuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c31a9eb54997:0xae121ca5b6d826c5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGeWFVazRSM2haTlZJNFowVkxOVjlCUW14dVIxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Electric, instantaneous, efficient\nThese are 3 words I would use to describe the service at Sichuan street food.\nI have long wanted to go and I finally dined here. With my family we ordered a myriad of dishes, each one was authentic, flavorful, and of course delicious.\nSome of the best Chinese food I can recommend you.\nI recommend for sure the Dan Dan noodles, the egg fried rice, the cumin lamb, diced chicken with spicy chilies, and green beans.\n10/10", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Electric, instantaneous, efficient\nThese are 3 words I would use to describe the service at Sichuan street food.\nI have long wanted to go and I finally dined here. With my family we ordered a myriad of dishes, each one was authentic, flavorful, and of course delicious.\nSome of the best Chinese food I can recommend you.\nI recommend for sure the Dan Dan noodles, the egg fried rice, the cumin lamb, diced chicken with spicy chilies, and green beans.\n10/10", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "MÖzil 99 (Mo)", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114875727385948510043/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVF03Mn32kf1Urk_89ZHmqkqeW9FJ5zALxcu06jWqMOb3KEV4G2=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-03T02:35:06.237114045Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGeWFVazRSM2haTlZJNFowVkxOVjlCUW14dVIxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGeWFVazRSM2haTlZJNFowVkxOVjlCUW14dVIxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c31a9eb54997:0xae121ca5b6d826c5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwNmRqUmZNRGxYWVZaM1NWQnVhVFIzTm5NMGNHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing food and amazing service. Small family owned placed. Everyone was really friendly and the food, omg the food. Do yourself a favor and get the diced chicken with chilies.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing food and amazing service. Small family owned placed. Everyone was really friendly and the food, omg the food. Do yourself a favor and get the diced chicken with chilies.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lisa Anderson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112091018855043002530/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWC2IWurj8Dd_ajdILhYP1gMqNimp53pP7qbpDN21mJx1IqZv_ZWw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T21:08:49.377759176Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwNmRqUmZNRGxYWVZaM1NWQnVhVFIzTm5NMGNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwNmRqUmZNRGxYWVZaM1NWQnVhVFIzTm5NMGNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c31a9eb54997:0xae121ca5b6d826c5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kbFFuSnBaVFZvTWtwbVlrWkdiMW90YUhsU1RtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Located on the north side of Green Street. Street parking only. Next to L’moon Creamery.\nIt’s been years since I’ve had authentic Sichuan food. When I think of the ingredients and flavors in mind, they bring it to life here in Pasadena. For such a small restaurant, they have quite the number of items available on the menu. Only a handful of tables inside. “Street food” is meant to be eaten quickly or on the go. The food comes out fast. So even if there’s not a lot of seating, the turnover is high. I was very happy to try this place and I will definitely be coming back to try more of their food.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Located on the north side of Green Street. Street parking only. Next to L’moon Creamery.\nIt’s been years since I’ve had authentic Sichuan food. When I think of the ingredients and flavors in mind, they bring it to life here in Pasadena. For such a small restaurant, they have quite the number of items available on the menu. Only a handful of tables inside. “Street food” is meant to be eaten quickly or on the go. The food comes out fast. So even if there’s not a lot of seating, the turnover is high. I was very happy to try this place and I will definitely be coming back to try more of their food.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "J C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114036338513962009903/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyJ7wsnrwcn9ddlXaB9sUX1I5Qs0Q3nlYRtbrcY0npY0X1VMscDg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-24T07:16:34.843101040Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kbFFuSnBaVFZvTWtwbVlrWkdiMW90YUhsU1RtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kbFFuSnBaVFZvTWtwbVlrWkdiMW90YUhsU1RtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c31a9eb54997:0xae121ca5b6d826c5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJl0m1nhrDwoARxSbYtqUcEq4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxdlpVeHdSVlJqUlVoc1JIbE5kMUU1TTJvemJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This Sichuan restaurant in Los Angeles is amazing ， you can even choose your spice level! The chef’s skills are top-notch, and every dish gives me that warm feeling of being back home. I came a bit late today, so the bullfrog was sold out, but luckily they still had pork kidney, which was fantastic. Great service too ， highly recommended!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This Sichuan restaurant in Los Angeles is amazing ， you can even choose your spice level! The chef’s skills are top-notch, and every dish gives me that warm feeling of being back home. I came a bit late today, so the bullfrog was sold out, but luckily they still had pork kidney, which was fantastic. Great service too ， highly recommended!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "loud cat", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107097318521701787355/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsvrhbDZp7bshpCorJArZBK4GGs81fR0XFT1x8OCEzopxHoOo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-28T06:07:05.240701581Z", "